            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Ahead of the match, Barcelona coach Hansi Flick criticized Spain's national team management over the handling of Lamine Yamal's injury. Spain coach Luis de la Fuente responded by saying he was "not interested" in the criticism.</p>
