            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">Oklahoma Superintendent of Public Instruction Ryan Walters has announced significant new education policies that are generating discussion across the state.</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">In mid 2025, board members alleged that during a private meeting, Walters displayed nude images on a television in his office. Walters denied the accusations, insisting the claims were lies and part of a coordinated attempt to discredit him.</p>
            <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">The Oklahoma County Sheriff and the State Bureau of Investigation are involved; the investigation is still ongoing and not yet concluded. Official review of the television hardware showed that the TV had streaming, antenna, and cable capabilities.</p>
